snippet.title: Let's Play Creatures Village
snippet.description:
Oof. It's an hour of Creatures Village, condensed into 25 minutes of playing-a-game-I-strongly-dislike fun! Yay.
---
Thank you so much for watching! As usual, you are welcome to leave suggestions for how I can improve my videos. If you like my videos, make sure to like, comment and subscribe!
